    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board SKL-L06 (900mm x 500mm)",
    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Free Shipping in Australia</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span><meta charset=\"utf-8\"> <meta charset=\"utf-8\">SeaKing SKL-L06</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The SeaKing SKL-L06 is a heavy-duty bait board designed for serious anglers, featuring integrated </span><span>cup holders, a knife tray, and a generously sized storage sink that spans nearly the entire length of </span><span>the board. With the widest variety of mounting points available, these boards accommodate vessels of </span><span>all sizes. Handcrafted using premium composite materials, they boast a UV resistant PE plastic </span><span>cutting board for durability and longevity on the water. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Tailored for larger boats, these bait boards are </span><span>ideal for tasks like cubing pilchards or preparing squid for broadbill fishing, ensuring you have the </span><span>necessary tools and space for successful fishing adventures.</span><strong></strong></p>",
